Poor blood pressure control in general practice: in search of explanations.

Nicod√®me R(1), Albessard A, Amar J, Chamontin B, Lang T.

Author information:
(1)D√©partement universitaire de m√©decine g√©n√©rale, facult√© de m√©decine, CHU de 
