Prospective cost-effectiveness analysis of cetuximab in metastatic colorectal 
cancer: evaluation of National Cancer Institute of Canada Clinical Trials Group 
CO.17 trial.

Mittmann N(1), Au HJ, Tu D, O'Callaghan CJ, Isogai PK, Karapetis CS, Zalcberg 
JR, Evans WK, Moore MJ, Siddiqui J, Findlay B, Colwell B, Simes J, Gibbs P, 
Links M, Tebbutt NC, Jonker DJ; Working Group on Economic Analysis of National 
Cancer Institute of Canada Clinical Trials Group; Australasian Gastrointestinal 
